            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Gaio Clementis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Clementi Eraconis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Publio Clementis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Vectinia Enimanui <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>iugi</abbr></expan> et fileis <note>sic</note> et <lb n="6"/>Posila Quarta Quinta <lb n="7"/>patri et fratribus <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>eritis</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fundstelle strittig. Weitere Angaben: sur la Colline de Revel ou de l&amp;apos;Abadie.</p>
            </div>
